const ExpenseForm = () =>{
    return (
        <form>
            <label>
            Title:
            <input type='text'></input>
            </label>
            <label>
            Amount:
            <input type='number'></input>
            </label>
            <label>
            Date:
            <input type='date'></input>
            </label>
        </form>
    )
}
export default ExpenseForm;
